#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:2
msgid "系统概览与界面导航"
msgstr "System Overview and Navigation"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:4
msgid "本页介绍 AOI 系统的整体架构、顶层界面导航逻辑，以及首次启动时的登录操作与启动画面。面向所有角色（管理员、操作员、编程人员）。"
msgstr ""
"This page covers the AOI system's overall architecture, top-level "
"navigation, and the login and startup screens on first launch. It is for "
"all roles (administrator, operator, programmer)."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:16
msgid "访问系统"
msgstr "Accessing the System"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:18
msgid ""
"浏览器直接访问系统根路径（默认 "
"``http://localhost:3005/``），或在桌面点击启动器后浏览器自动打开。未登录时会自动跳转至登录页。"
msgstr ""
"Open the system root path in a browser (default "
"``http://localhost:3005/``), or click the desktop launcher to open it "
"automatically. If you are not logged in, you are redirected to the login "
"page."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:-1
msgid "AOI 系统登录页"
msgstr "AOI system login page"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:25
msgid "系统整体布局"
msgstr "Overall Layout"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:27
msgid "登录后，所有页面共享一个固定的顶部导航栏。导航栏包含以下元素："
msgstr "After login, every page shares a fixed top navigation bar. It contains:"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:29
msgid ""
"**左上角 Logo / 系统名称**：点击可随时从任何页面返回 :ui-tab:`主页`。在 :ui-tab:`设置` 和 :ui-"
"btn:`工作列表` 页面，名称旁会额外显示当前页面的标签；在 :ui-tab:`产品编程页面`，会在名称旁追加正在编程的产品名称。"
msgstr ""
"**Top-left logo / system name**: click it to return to the :ui-tab:`Home`"
" page from anywhere. On the :ui-tab:`Settings` and :ui-btn:`Work List` "
"pages, the current page's label is shown next to the name; on the :ui-"
"tab:`Product Programming Page`, the name of the product being programmed "
"is appended."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:30
msgid "**右上角功能区**：从左到右依次为磁盘用量指示器、用于进入 :ui-tab:`设置` 的 :ui-btn:`齿轮图标`，以及当前登录的用户名。"
msgstr ""
"**Top-right area**: from left to right, a disk-usage indicator, the :ui-"
"btn:`gear icon` (which opens :ui-tab:`Settings`), and the current user's "
"name."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:34
msgid "检测会话运行期间，点击 :ui-btn:`齿轮图标` 会弹出提示，告知设置暂不可用；需先停止检测任务后再进入设置。"
msgstr ""
"While an inspection session is running, clicking the :ui-btn:`gear icon` "
"shows a notice that Settings is temporarily unavailable; stop the "
"inspection task first, then open Settings."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:-1
#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:37
msgid "登录页面"
msgstr "Login Page"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:43
msgid "登录页包含以下控件："
msgstr "The login page has these controls:"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:45
msgid ":ui-param:`用户名`：输入账户名称。"
msgstr ":ui-param:`Username`: enter the account name."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:46
msgid ":ui-param:`密码`：输入账户密码，支持按回车键直接提交。"
msgstr ":ui-param:`Password`: enter the account password; press Enter to submit."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:47
msgid ":ui-btn:`登录`：提交凭据，验证通过后跳转至 :ui-tab:`主页`。"
msgstr ""
":ui-btn:`Log In`: submit credentials; on success you go to the :ui-"
"tab:`Home` page."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:48
msgid ""
":ui-btn:`更改主机地址`：打开主机地址配置弹窗，用于修改后端服务器地址（默认 "
"``http://localhost:8000/``）。如需从其他设备访问，可在此将 ``localhost`` 替换为目标机器的 IP 地址。"
msgstr ""
":ui-btn:`Change Host Address`: opens the host-address dialog to change "
"the backend server address (default ``http://localhost:8000/``). To "
"access from another device, replace ``localhost`` with the target "
"machine's IP address."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:50
msgid "界面语言可在登录后于 :ui-tab:`系统设置` → :ui-tab:`语言` 中切换（:ui-opt:`中文` / :ui-opt:`英文`）。"
msgstr ""
"After login, switch the UI language under :ui-tab:`System Settings` → "
":ui-tab:`Language` (:ui-opt:`中文` / :ui-opt:`English`)."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:-1
msgid "更改主机地址弹窗"
msgstr "Change host address dialog"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:57
msgid "用户角色"
msgstr "User Roles"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:59
msgid "系统内置三种用户角色，每种角色对应不同的操作权限："
msgstr "The system has three built-in user roles, each with different permissions:"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:61
msgid ""
"**管理员（ADMIN）**：拥有全部权限，包括 :ui-tab:`团队` "
"管理（创建/删除账户、分配角色）、所有系统设置项，以及主页上的全部功能区（包括产品编程入口 :ui-btn:`训练PCBA` 和 :ui-"
"btn:`工作列表`）。"
msgstr ""
"**Administrator (ADMIN)**: full permissions, including :ui-tab:`Team` "
"management (create/delete accounts, assign roles), all system settings, "
"and every area on the home page (including the product-programming entry "
":ui-btn:`Teach PCBA` and :ui-btn:`Work List`)."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:62
msgid ""
"**编程人员（PROGRAMMER）**：可使用产品编程（:ui-btn:`训练PCBA`）和检测相关功能，并访问大多数系统设置，但无法访问 "
":ui-tab:`团队` 管理页面。"
msgstr ""
"**Programmer (PROGRAMMER)**: can use product programming (:ui-btn:`Teach "
"PCBA`) and inspection features, and access most system settings, but "
"cannot open the :ui-tab:`Team` management page."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:63
msgid ""
"**操作员（OPERATOR）**：仅可执行检测操作（启动/停止检测任务、查看 :ui-"
"btn:`工作列表`），不可访问产品编程入口，且系统设置中多数高级选项对操作员不可用。"
msgstr ""
"**Operator (OPERATOR)**: can only run inspection (start/stop inspection "
"tasks, view the :ui-btn:`Work List`), cannot access product programming, "
"and most advanced system settings are unavailable."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:65
msgid "管理员账户在系统部署时提供，默认用户名为 **admin**。账户管理请进入设置页的 :ui-tab:`团队` 分组（仅管理员可见）。"
msgstr ""
"The administrator account is provided at deployment; the default username"
" is **admin**. Manage accounts in the :ui-tab:`Team` group of the "
"Settings page (visible to administrators only)."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:68
msgid "系统初始化页面"
msgstr "System Initializing Page"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:70
msgid "系统首次启动或后端服务尚未就绪时，浏览器会进入 **系统初始化中…** 等待页面。页面显示初始化进度或连接状态，并提供两个操作按钮："
msgstr ""
"On first launch, or while the backend is not yet ready, the browser shows"
" a **System Initializing…** waiting page. It displays initialization "
"progress or connection status and offers two buttons:"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:72
msgid ":ui-btn:`刷新`：重新加载页面，重新尝试连接后端。"
msgstr ":ui-btn:`Refresh`: reload the page and retry the backend connection."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:73
msgid ":ui-btn:`更改主机地址`：在后端地址填写有误时，可打开主机地址弹窗重新配置。"
msgstr ""
":ui-btn:`Change Host Address`: if the backend address is wrong, open the "
"host-address dialog to reconfigure it."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:75
msgid "当后端初始化完成后，系统将自动根据登录状态跳转：令牌有效则直接进入主页，令牌已过期则跳转至登录页。"
msgstr ""
"Once the backend finishes initializing, the system redirects based on "
"login state: a valid token goes straight to the home page; an expired "
"token goes to the login page."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:78
msgid "注意事项"
msgstr "Notes"

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:82
msgid ""
"检测会话进行中，点击顶部导航栏的 Logo 返回主页、或点击 :ui-btn:`齿轮图标` "
"进入设置时，若当前正在复检页面且有未完成的确认操作，系统会先弹出确认弹窗，待操作员确认后再执行导航，以防止意外丢失检测数据。"
msgstr ""
"While an inspection session is running, if you click the top-bar logo to "
"return home or the :ui-btn:`gear icon` to open Settings while on the "
"review page with an unfinished confirmation, the system first shows a "
"confirmation dialog and waits for the operator before navigating, to "
"avoid losing inspection data."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:83
msgid "角色权限在登录时由服务器签发的 JWT 令牌确定，切换权限需重新以对应账户登录。"
msgstr ""
"Role permissions are set by the server-issued JWT token at login; to "
"change permissions, log in again with the appropriate account."

#: ../../source/introduce/overview/index.rst:87
msgid ":ref:`快速开始`"
msgstr ":ref:`快速开始`"

